title: DPS BestOf
itunes:title: DPS BestOf
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Chris Mannix about the Nets' early exit from the playoffs. Who deserves the blame? Chris Simms discusses the Deebo Samuel situation. Does he think we'll see Deebo get traded. And Nick Wright tells us which current players he thinks will end up Top 10 all-time. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
